Title: Easmark
Text: Eomer the Marchall of the Mark needs help in the war against Saruman.He ask me to fight with him and free the Eaastmark (Eastemneth).I will meet him at the bottom of the old watchtower.
CompleteText: We did it! All the Uruk Captains are dead and the area is save again!A little bit of hope for the people of Rohan in this war against Isengard!I should continue my journey and see how i can help the people of middleearth even more.
